data.title: It only cost $200,000! Did you know these low-budget movies became HUGE box office hits?
data.meta_description: Some of the most successful and popular films over the past decades had REALLY low budgets for their makings. You will be surprised to learn which famous titles were produced with only a couple of dollars, but ended up surpassing all limits with their box-office earnings!
